events.question:
Hellooooo! I’m Rafa, Captain for the Magical Girl Corps!
Is your day going OK so far?

events.choice: Going good! Just getting some stuff for today!

events.question:
Cool! What do you have planned? Wait, sorry I don’t have time for that right now...
I just needed to tell everyone on the block that a humongous monster might come here and that you should probably go somewhere else for now. Is that OK?

events.choice: Of course! I’ll just finish up my errands and I’ll go somewhere safe. Thank you!
Yeah, sure. Thanks for the heads up!

events.question:
Well, I’m dealing with a big monster instead of hanging out with my girlfriend or reading my books, what a bummer!
By the way, that monster might come this way so find somewhere safe to go, OK?

events.choice: Oh OK, thank you for telling me! Bye!
Cool, I’ll go do that. Bye!
